iv><div>https://www.thegamer.com/helldivers-2-d10-organiser-fired-doxxed/</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/I543AhA.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://www.gosugamers.net/entertainment/news/78095-helldivers-2-devs-and-sony-condemn-death-threats-after-d10-dev-challenge-charity-event-spirals

The user (u/Key_Complex_150) was fired primarily because his employer deemed him a safety and liability risk due to the extreme harassment campaign targeting the company.
According to the details shared by the victim and the community:
